  <li><abbr title="U.S. Geological Survey">USGS</abbr> <abbr title="Priority Ecosystems Science">Priority Ecosystem Science (PES)</abbr> funding in <abbr title="Fiscal Year 2013">FY13</abbr> was to multiple principal investigators in support for EDEN research efforts. This level of support is expected to be continued in <abbr title="Fiscal Year 2014">FY14</abbr> with a potential 5-10% cut.</li>
</ul>
